    "b440: polished the elite/boss combat loom after the b439 fix. (1) The VICTORY frame no longer drops the loom -- a felled elite kept rendering as a 96px in-flow sprite that grew the monster box and clipped the player box below it; it now reuses the fight's loom styling (slot-capped panel height + the over-the-HUD overlay), so the dead foe still towers on the LEFT over the stats bar instead of expanding the panel. (2) The defeat grayscale fade now also greys the loom overlay -- when looming, the visible sprite IS the overlay (the in-flow canvas is hidden), so without this the dead-monster fade did nothing. (3) Loomed sprites now anchor to the left edge of their slot.",
